data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Pride of ownership 5 BD/3BA home in quiet, new neighborhood.  The main floor has a 5th bedroom/addl. office and an open kitchen to living room w/gas fireplace.  Granite/tile countertops, laminate & tile flooring throughout.  Custom water filtration system & concrete RV Pad behind closed gate. Home includes smart home technology adding convenience.  No close neighbors to the North give a sense of privacy in the backyard.  A must see!  Appointment necessary.
